I beg to forward to your Excellency [
   two
] copy of the 37 Number of my fragmenta, in which both the genera Cardvillia & Darlingia are now for the first time diagnostified. In begging your Excellency, acceptance of the same and in asking to forward kindly one of the prints to the right honorable minister at the head of the Colonial affairs, I wished also to express my deep gratification for her majesty having in her mildness & benign generosity condescended to identify her illustrious name with the philanthropic work of the Australian Ladies.
